Package cycleguard.database.stats

Class UserStats

java.lang.Object
cycleguard.database.AbstractDatabaseEntry
cycleguard.database.AbstractDatabaseUserEntry
cycleguard.database.stats.UserStats
public final class UserStats extends AbstractDatabaseUserEntry
DynamoDbBean linking a username to that user's full statistics.
  • accountCreationTime - Seconds after epoch when account was created
  • totalDistance - Total distance traveled by the user
  • totalTime - Total time user spent biking
  • bestPackGoalProgress - Best pack goal progress achieved by any of user's previous or current packs
  • lastRideDay - Highest seconds after epoch when user took a ride
  • rideStreak - Current daily ride streak of user
  • bestStreak - Best daily ride streak of user
